From 8a1face955aa7fc98fbcae2217a99eb940161d01 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date: Thu, 16 Jul 2026 04:47:41 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] feat: refresh brand identity and add a real login screen
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

- Redesign the logo/favicon mark (industrial hexagon seal on the
  existing navy/gold identity) and use it on the boot screen.
- Add login.html: a per-user username/password screen for all roles,
  built in the new identity, ready to call /api/auth/login once that
  route exists.
- Draft a Supabase migration (005) adding username/password_hash to
  app_users, login verification RPCs, and an employee_dues ledger table
  for the employee self-service view — no new Vercel function wired yet
  so this doesn't reopen the Hobby 12-function limit PR #6 is fixing.
